targets.expr:
sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

((avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])  
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName))
/(avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])     
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)) != NaN ) OR on() vector(0)

(sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName) *100)
/ sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName=~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

(avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])  
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_sum{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName))
/(avg(
  max_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])     
  - min_over_time(jmeter_response_time_count{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName))

(sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName) *100)

/ sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{requestName!~".+XX.*", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{ projectName="$group",testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+",requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group",requestStatus="FAIL", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+",requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
)
/ sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+"}[${__range_s}s])
)

sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID",requestName=~".+XX.+", requestStatus="FAIL"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, requestName)

sum(
  max_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group",requestName!~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", responseMessage!~"^Number.+", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
  - min_over_time(jmeter_requests{projectName="$group",requestName!~".+XX.*", requestStatus="FAIL", responseMessage!~"^Number.+", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[${__range_s}s])
) by (runId, responseCode, responseMessage)

panels.title: TPS - by operations nested in the transaction

targets.expr:
sum(rate(jmeter_response_time_sum{parent=~'$transaction', isTransaction="false", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[$__interval]))by(requestName)
/ sum(rate(jmeter_response_time_count{parent=~'$transaction', isTransaction="false", testName="$project", runId = "$RunID"}[$__interval]))by(requestName)
